ðŸ”¹ 3. Function (Input â†’ Output)

âœ” Takes input
âœ” Returns output

import java.util.*;
import java.util.function.Function;

class solution {
    public static void main (String[] args){
        Function<Integer,Integer> f = n-> n * n;

        System.out.println(f.apply(5));


    }
}

Output:

25


