ðŸ”¹ 4. Supplier (Only output)

âœ” No input
âœ” Returns output

import java.util.*;
import java.util.function.Supplier;

class solution {
    public static void main (String[] args){
       Supplier<String> s = () -> "hello";

        System.out.println(s.get());

    }
}

Output:

Java 8


Use case:
ðŸ‘‰ value generation

